race.comment: ADAPTATION (4) progressed nicely beaten 1.5 lengths here stepping up to 1500m. Will have taken further fitness and learning and is drawn to advantage. The in-form Latham rides for the first time. Looks like third time the charm. SUN TO ME (6) led and found one 1L too good here, heavily bet over 1500m. Is busting to win and has a handy 2kg claim and a positive gate. Will give a big sight again. VELARIS (3) is an improver better suited at the provincials. Races handy and is ready for the mile. GARRIX (5) from the same yard comes back a bit in trip. His effort two back at Kembla Grange hinted at better things to come.
